<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BlogNest</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="home.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Nabla&family=Roboto&family=Roboto+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="nav">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/img/logo.png" alt="Logo">
        </div>

        <div class="navbar">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="head">
        <div class="head-one head-style">
            <h1>Explore, Connect, Inspire:</h1>
            <h1>Welcome to Our Blogging Haven!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="head-two head-style">
            <div class="box">
                <img src="/img/blog_card.jpg" alt="card">;
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="content-heading">Diverse Blogging Community</div>
            <div class="content-blog">
                <h2>Greetings and a warm welcome to our vibrant blogging community!</h2>
                <p>Whether you're a seasoned wordsmith or embarking on your writing adventure, you've discovered a haven to express your thoughts, share experiences, and weave compelling stories for the world to savor.</p>
                <p>Our platform thrives on cultivating a rich tapestry of diverse voices, innovative ideas, and unique perspectives. Dive into the array of categories, immerse yourself in inspiring articles, and forge connections with fellow bloggers who, like you, are passionate about shaping this dynamic space.</p>
                <h3>Cheers to the exciting journey ahead! <span class="red-heart">&hearts;</span></h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="/img/what_your_story.jpg" alt="Logo">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="extra"></div>

    <div class="footer">
        <div class="space"></div>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="about footer-boxes">
                <img src="/img/logo.png" alt="Logo">
                <h3>Where voices unite, stories flourish, and connections inspire! <span class="red-heart">&hearts;</span></h3>
            </div>
            <div class="links footer-boxes">
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                    <a href="#">Home</a>
                </div><br>
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                    <a href="#">About</a>
                </div><br>
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                    <a href="#">Services</a>
                </div><br>
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                    <a href="#">Contact</a>
                </div><br>
            </div>
            <div class="content footer-boxes">
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i>
                    <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                </div><br>
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-square-instagram"></i>
                    <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                </div><br>
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i>
                    <a href="#">Linkedin</a>
                </div><br>
                <div>
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>
                    <a href="#">Youtube</a>
                </div><br>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>